                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-base mb-3">Live Configuration</h3>
                            <p class="text-base-content/70">
                                Adjust protection rules, sensitivity levels, and blocking strategies in real-time without downtime. A/B test security policies and instantly rollback changes.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dedicated Support -->
            <div class="card bg-base-200 border-2 border-primary/20 hover:border-primary transition-all">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-base mb-3">Dedicated Support</h3>
                            <p class="text-base-content/70">
                                24/7 priority support with dedicated security engineers, Slack/Teams integration, custom SLA agreements, and proactive threat intelligence updates.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- API & Integrations -->
            <div class="card bg-base-200 border-2 border-secondary/20 hover:border-secondary transition-all">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 text-secondary">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-base mb-3">API & Integrations</h3>
                            <p class="text-base-content/70">
                                RESTful API, GraphQL endpoints, webhooks, and native integrations with popular platforms. Custom integration support for legacy systems.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Compliance & Security -->
            <div class="card bg-base-200 border-2 border-accent/20 hover:border-accent transition-all">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 text-accent">
