                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="card-title text-base mb-3">Compliance & Security</h3>
                            <p class="text-base-content/70">
                                SOC 2 Type II certified, GDPR compliant, zero-PII architecture, audit logs, data residency options, and enterprise SSO support.
